Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad0\fad(1000,1000)\pos(415,211)}Scénář         Nakajima Takehiro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(129,87)\shad0\fad(1000,1000)}Hudba          Hisaishi Joe
